to describe the workspace, while `/portal/login/page.tsx` can house the login form, so I'll start with changes there.\n\n\n**Refining Public Landing Page**\n\nI've made progress on `/portal/page.tsx`, deciding to make it the premium public landing page with `/portal/login` as the login path. I'm now structuring it with `InnerPageShell`, a custom hero, a secure narrative, the interactive module selector, a bento grid, security parameters, and a prominent \"Enclave Notice\" box.\n\n\n"}}
